---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Pending Guidance Requests"
permalink: "/pending-guidance/"
class: guidance
---

<section class="section-intro">
  <p>These topics have been identified as needing additional clarification or guidance from regulatory bodies. The FAQ Task Force is actively working to develop these guidance requests.</p>
</section>

<nav class="card-grid">
  {% for item in data.guidance %}
    <a href="{{ item.permalink }}" class="card">
      <h2>{{ item.title | markdownInline | safe }}</h2>
      {% if item.data.status %}
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{ item.data.status | replace('-', ' ') | title }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      {% if item.relatedFaqs and item.relatedFaqs.length > 0 %}
        <p>{{ item.relatedFaqs.length }} related FAQ{{ 's' if item.relatedFaqs.length != 1 }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</nav>
